<h4 class="title text-sm p-5 px-0 xl:px-5 font-normal tracking-widest uppercase xl:-ml-5">More from SOFREP</h4>
<div class="related md:flex xl:-mx-2 flex-wrap">
<div class="news-box md:px-2 md:w-1/3">
